result.name: 2009-defra-mb0102-2b-distribution-of-mobile-species-half-rectangle-resolution-layer
result.notes:
The data for 40 highly mobile species within this layer are distributed at a half ICES rectangle resolution (0.5 x 0.5 degrees) and have been obtained from Aqua maps and expert knowledge, primarily from A Wheeler.
     To provide mathematically modeled species distributions combined with and quality assured by expert knowledge.
